  "title": "Product Manager",
  "description": "<p>• Responsible for products promotion of the product line assigned.</p><p>• To achieve revenue and design target as set by Principal and Company in SEA region.</p><p>• Maintain healthy inventory level, maximize GP performance as set by Company.</p><p>• Align company’s strategy with Principal’s strategy and maintain good rapport with Principal.</p><p>• Effectively carry out MARCOM activities.</p><p>• Any other related projects/duties which not indicated above will be assigned by the superior from time to time</p><p><strong>EDUCATION AND EXPERIENCE</strong></p><p>• Diploma/Degree in Electronics Electrical Engineering</p><p>• Minimum 4 years of relevant working experience in product marketing industry.</p><p><strong>KNOWLEDGE, SKILLS, ABILITIES</strong></p><p>• Proficient in MS Office (Teams, Excel, Power Point and Word)</p><p>• Good knowledge of the industry, good resources in terms of customers, manufacturers and competitors.</p><p>• Effective communication skills, good inter-personal skills and good analytical skills.</p><p>• Creativity and have initiative to learn.</p><p>• Able to work under stress</p><p>• Self-motivated, self-driven and objective oriented.</p>",
